OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Ffading to leave a largely dry night
OL,7,Fwith lengthy clear spells, although
OL,8,Fchance of a few coastal showers
OL,9,Flingering. Turning chilly inland with
OL,10,Flight winds and a patchy frost in
OL,11,Fprone rural spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FLargely dry and bright,
OL,14,Fafter a chilly start. Cloud increasing
OL,15,Ffrom the west during the late
OL,16,Fafternoon, bringing some outbreaks of
OL,17,Frain across all parts through the
OL,18,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
