OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FRain
OL,6,Fclearing early Sunday then drier and
OL,7,Fbrighter. Chance of showers later.
OL,8,FMonday, variable cloud and showers.
OL,9,FRain and strong winds overnight,
OL,10,Fclearing Tuesday morning. Showers
OL,11,Ffollowing and breezy.
